{"tid":711993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳啟泰d frd】女子飲狗尿，聲稱能醫青春痘。","createTime":"2018-06-21T22:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T13:29:35.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c906b4e81dcad6eefd1d4645a64d1b689f69142","tid":711993,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:45:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xZbyCvHUsio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxZbyCvHUsio&d=IoZT6UV6PEEN1dOyYelu0Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6f4504af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xZbyCvHUsio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國一名女子近日上傳一段影片，片中她接了自家寵物狗狗的尿來喝，還自稱狗尿富含營養，能治好青春痘，甚至是癌症。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這名女子拍片錄下她接下寵物狗狗的尿之後，當場一飲而盡，她強調走「自然路線」，<span style=\"color: red;\">更宣稱狗尿富含維他命A、E還有鈣質</span>。女子更說，就在她喝狗尿之前，她很憂鬱、心情容易沮喪，甚至長滿青春痘，但喝下狗尿後，一切都好轉。她相信喝狗尿可以治好青春痘，甚至是癌症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180621/640_aa8881d0b4025b6c1223f1842b35c6c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180621%2F640_aa8881d0b4025b6c1223f1842b35c6c6.jpg&h=ca63f4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180621/640_bb3ef121d37550f465c5ec93fb726873.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180621%2F640_bb3ef121d37550f465c5ec93fb726873.jpg&h=956e5ede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92a14e093950ec17656eb417b7ec62064ab06447","tid":711993,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:46:08.000Z","msg":"噉俾狗屌係咪個屄會緊啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae45818ea131da3ecb4fbd7e0797339a311f898c","tid":711993,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20